    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "2019 Honda Accord EX-L. This vehicle is in poor condition. It has significant mechanical issues that will require attention, noticeable interior wear including stains and damage, and exterior damage such as scratches, dents, or paint issues. Sold as-is. Best suited for buyers prepared to invest in repairs.",
